{"tid":128601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉見選委嘆社會多怨氣：開始明白點解佢哋佔中","createTime":"2017-02-21T03:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T12:47:39.000Z","uid":48093,"like":6,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b79fb030aa19960c400eb6205031bb9a9ad5c595","tid":128601,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170221/large/1487645529_0788.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170221%2Flarge%2F1487645529_0788.jpg&h=dd48af04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首參選人葉劉淑儀早上接受電台節目電話訪問時表示，今次選舉經驗猶如進行了一場大型社會調查研究，自己接觸到各界別人士包括社會福利、殘疾人士、長者、醫務衞生等，才知原來服務多方面落後，慨嘆「社會真係好多怨氣」。她更指見過民主派「真普聯」19名醫生選委，當中有人曾參與佔領，「我開始明白點解佢哋去佔中，對我嚟講係好寶貴嘅經驗」。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉早前明言選情好嚴峻，她感謝選委明知道她處於弱勢仍願意見她，指自己多了很多朋友。她透露，參選前已有人問她若輸了會如何，她認為選舉不是贏就是輸，更暗寸被指獲中央欽點的對手林鄭月娥「極少有人是未有政綱就以為一定贏的」。她強調參選是要爭取政治理想、實現抱負、多了解社會，稱已經做到。"},{"pid":"7926762babc8104137131f3710e67956e6e0a164","tid":128601,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:05:17.000Z","msg":"條撚屌知道唔夠林鄭爭就開始9up"},{"pid":"36a7ae3dae95b28a08262eb8a63a0b5f969ee138","tid":128601,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:05:22.000Z","msg":"開始明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9f6a732b5bd89118ccd09b5753e65c89dea276","tid":128601,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:06:16.000Z","msg":"想攞泛民票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c415681b6a23332e69936e279e6d94299ecc68","tid":128601,"uid":20723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:06:44.000Z","msg":"洗底加分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a