\n點知無啦啦張德江打埋開口牌要人支持林病 佢就奶撚哂野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n葉劉就柒下柒下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n林鄭個勢一路lead住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你睇返689喺鏡頭下見諾基亞，都成隻狗咁唯唯諾諾，你就會想像到佢同淋病見到京官，一定係成個奴才咁瀨晒鞋底。強國呢類奴才DNA國家，最buy呢類下屬。<br />\n你睇葉劉份人，一定做唔到，咁你就明點解西環會支持淋病唔理葉劉。"},{"pid":"3c8d63a039b527ea21beebf244894ff160461699","tid":128601,"uid":27249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:19:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">港豬：正啊喂，all in 支持葉劉，課金 課金！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e0cc6f80a5343a9be0015a3277073fe196dc88","tid":128601,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:19:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實泛民策略上應該畀提名佢入<br />\n<br />\n佢同林鄭票源重疊，有機會界票<br />\n而且佢委屈咁耐，入閘實咬住林鄭<br />\n反而送胡、曾，會提高攬炒機會</blockquote><br />\n完全同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n提名長毛食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\non9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38d99efa8a4513bf38dccca6fff1cce6a8105bc","tid":128601,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:27:20.000Z","msg":"其實我唔明點解佔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當初又話反對831重啟政改 依家啲黃絲一見到曾俊華就濕曬咁 明明條友推23條兼堅持831<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁當初佔黎為咩啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfed50825f21b7807bb0e2f56aab87446634c987","tid":128601,"uid":34058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T05:28:36.000Z","msg":"人之將死 其言也善"},